test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (3 == 3 and 3 == 3 and 2 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x756d7ff6dc80>([51])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x756d7ff6dc80> = [[1, 51], [1, 51, 1], [51], [51, 1], [1, 51], [1, 51, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x756d7ff6dc80>([1, 51])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x756d7ff6dc80> = [[1, 51], [1, 51, 1], [51], [51, 1], [1, 51], [1, 51, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x756d7ff6dc80>([51, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x756d7ff6dc80> = [[1, 51], [1, 51, 1], [51], [51, 1], [1, 51], [1, 51, 1], ...].count

 +  where 1 = <built-in function prod>([])
